---
title: Self Service | DIY | Help Center | Live Chat – NHANCE NOW
"description": "Empower customers to resolve their own issues. Deploy digital self-service tools, Do-It-Yourself modules, Live Chat Solutions, Configure Help center with FAQs."
header: app-function
---
extends layouts/_layout
block content
  .app-function.support.app-function-scroll
    section.app-function__intro
      .container
        .app-function__intro__content.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration='1s')
          img(src='img/app-function/support/support-human.png', srcset='img/app-function/support/support-human@2x.png 2x, img/app-function/support/support-human@3x.png 3x')
          .row.center-xs
            .col-md-8.col-sm-10.col-xs-12.start-xs
              .app-function__intro__block
                strong INSTACARE
                h1 On Demand & Conversational
                p Give customers your control to resolve queries on their own and get trained with knowledgebases and various DIY channels
    section.app-function__description
      .container
        p A modern customer wants control on how and when to resolve their issues, take training or simply learn about new features and functionalities. NHANCE NOW helps you deliver these through a variety of support channels which are self managing. It transfers control of the support services directly to customers and lets them control the frequency, pace and channel of choice.
    section.app-function__examples
      .container
        h2 Features
      .app-function__examples__content
        .container
          .app-function__examples__block.app-function__examples__block-1
            .row.middle-xs
              .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.last-xs
                #app-function-img-1.app-function__examples__block__img
                  img(src='img/app-function/support/instacare-img-01.png', srcset='img/app-function/support/instacare-img-01@2x.png 2x, img/app-function/support/instacare-img-01@3x.png 3x')
              .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.col-sm-offset-1.last-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration='1.5s')
                h3 Do it Yourself (DIY)
                p
                  | The future of product and services training is “doing it ourselves”. Provide rich media files, on-demand videos, digital documents, tips and tricks to assist customers gain knowledge about your products and services without any external aid.
                p.app-function__examples__block-2
                  | Eliminate the need of human resources for assisting customers and enable anytime, anywhere learning.
          .app-function__examples__block
            .row.middle-xs
              .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration='1.5s')
                h3 Help Center
                p
                  | Modern day customers are impatient. They need resolutions to their queries instantly. Provide instant help via troubleshooting videos, FAQs, remote video support to provide instant gratification to your customers.
                p.app-function__examples__block-3
                  | The self-service section can help reduce the load on your back-office teams by as much as 30%. It can also reduce field visit of technicians and support agents by as much as 70%.
              .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.col-sm-offset-1
                #app-function-img-2.app-function__examples__block__img
                  img(src='img/app-function/support/instacare-img-02.png', srcset='img/app-function/support/instacare-img-02@2x.png 2x, img/app-function/support/instacare-img-02@3x.png 3x')
          .app-function__examples__block
            .row.middle-xs
              .col-sm-6.col-xs-12.last-xs
                #app-function-img-3.app-function__examples__block__img
                  img(src='img/app-function/support/instacare-img-03.png', srcset='img/app-function/support/instacare-img-03@2x.png 2x, img/app-function/support/instacare-img-03@3x.png 3x')
              .col-sm-5.col-xs-12.col-sm-offset-1.last-sm.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration='1.5s')
                h3 Live Chat
                p
                  | Live chat is the best communication platform to offer a real-time support and response to your customers. It has higher satisfaction rates than email and phone.With instant connect to live chat agents and 24/7 availability it is the most non-intrusive channel for customers support enjoying wide popularity.
                p
                  | Live chat not only helps your customers start a conversation with you anytime, it also helps youto build long-term relationships with your existing customers.
    section.app-function__start
      .container
        h2 Start transforming your customers into life time promoters
        a.btn.btn-primary(href='#schedule', rel='modal:open') request a demo
